name: Spill Out
description:
This wall hanging is made of ceramic, glaze, oxides & glass. It's a very dimensional & textural piece. The background color is reddish-brown, turquoise glaze and royal blue glass. The concept came from an airplane view of the mountains & the sea. 

The dimensions: 12 1/2" diameter x 5 1/2" depth. 

It is to be hung by 2 nails or screws.

If you have any questions convo me.
Christine627@hotmail.com

Thank You!!

name: Wrapped
description:
This is an abstract wall sculpture made from clay. The glazes are blue and green, the background is a matte reddish brown, with black indents and red dots . It has copper wire that is wrapped around and through the piece. 

The dimensions are: 8 1/2" width x 18" long x 2" depth

If you have any questions convo me.

Thank You!!

name: Topical View Decorative Plate
description:
This sculptural piece is made of clay, glaze, oxides & glass. It can hung on the wall (it has picture wire attached on the back) or put in a plate holder so it can sit upright on your furniture. 

It's a very dimensional piece with lots of texture. The background colors are reddish-brown, turquoise glaze and glass.

The dimensions: 14" Diameter, 2 1/2" depth.

If you have any questions please convo me.

name: Tight Bud
description:
This piece is made of clay, glaze & lots of time! The background color is a creamy, ivory color with greenish-blue glazed tips. The "petals" have a little grey shadowing made from carefully applied oxides. 

This piece is a wall hanging sculpture. The dimensions are: 8 3/4" diameter x 4 1/2' depth.

It's to be hung by 2 nails or screws.
